{"tid":1267712,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"愛護香港力量約20人警總外集會支持警方執法","createTime":"2019-06-30T04:32:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T04:52:52.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"997cfefb8e9672bce482b5ae8c225fd85c626f7c","tid":1267712,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T04:32:13.000Z","msg":"「愛護香港力量」大約20人在警總外舉行撐警活動，秘書長李家家表示，有市民擲磚頭和用鐵支襲警，毀壞公物和包圍政府設施，因此支持警方執法。<br />\n<br />\n被問到應否就612金鐘衝突成立獨立調查委員會，她說，監警會的機制行之有效，若成立獨立調查委員會同時調查，到時出現兩個調查結果不知哪個作準。她表示，監警會過往亦有個案懲罰警員，認為是有效力。"},{"pid":"8abbf103e3ab62ae2290292e0943375bfb65af40","tid":1267712,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T04:33:46.000Z","msg":"又話3000人"},{"pid":"9d1bf1e2c593d60907cbd1522d064bcbd6bc7d51","tid":1267712,"uid":126731,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T04:38:49.000Z","msg":"2000萬人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f96e3d7173b9874a68b469afbc0619320918ab2","tid":1267712,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T04:39:44.000Z","msg":"維穩錢用哂去邊"},{"pid":"fdd53f846bb42a6f9ad7dec3fd11799628a835df","tid":1267712,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T04:43:32.000Z","msg":"2億人"},{"pid":"f9321053cef94478565d223c5fcb173c62336089","tid":1267712,"uid":120955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T04:45:07.000Z","msg":"維穩費明明成球㗎喎 落格落咗去邊"},{"pid":"ba6b237a0fabf8460c36d22e3cc385d49c560545","tid":1267712,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T04:46:42.000Z","msg":"20人分幾百萬真爽皮"},{"pid":"715a289fc26ce9a9c21b012bb41e1e5b34fe2161","tid":1267712,"uid":32325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba6b237a0fabf8460c36d22e3cc385d49c560545","tid":1267712,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T04:46:42.000Z","msg":"20人分幾百萬真爽皮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30